### Video API tests for Cursos
### Requires VS Code REST Client extension or compatible client
### Set variables below before running

@BASE_URL = http://localhost:8000/api
@TOKEN = REPLACE_WITH_BEARER_TOKEN
@COURSE_ID = 1

### 1) Init video upload
POST {{BASE_URL}}/admin/cursos/{{COURSE_ID}}/video/upload-init
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "contentType": "video/mp4"
}

### 2) Complete video upload
POST {{BASE_URL}}/admin/cursos/{{COURSE_ID}}/video/upload-complete
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### 3) Get playback info
GET {{BASE_URL}}/admin/cursos/{{COURSE_ID}}/video/playback
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### 4) Report playback progress
POST {{BASE_URL}}/admin/cursos/{{COURSE_ID}}/video/progress
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "position": 42.5
}
